     "words": ["machine", "readable"], "intent": "portability_request", "bonus": 2.5},
    {"_comment": "GDPR Art. 18 — pause processing distinguishes restriction from erasure",
     "words": ["stop", "processing"], "intent": "restriction_request", "bonus": 2.5},
    {"_comment": "GDPR Art. 21 — explicit objection phrasing",
