     "words": ["automated", "decision"], "intent": "adm_challenge_request", "bonus": 3.0},
    {"_comment": "Art. 22 / CPRA ADMT — human-review request routes ADM",
     "words": ["human", "review"], "intent": "adm_challenge_request", "bonus": 2.5},
    {"_comment": "GDPR Art. 16 — explicit rectification phrasing",
